31 of the student code of conduct, and possible threats to campus safety.
32 (3) Where to find reports regarding campus safety.
33 (4) The information required in this Subsection shall be updated in consultation
34 with campus or local law enforcement.
35 C.(1) The information shall be distributed as part of new student orientation and shall
36 be posted on an easily accessible page of each institution's website.
37 (2) If the student receiving the information required by Subsections B and C of
38 this Section is a minor, the information shall also be provided to his parent or legal
39 guardian.
